  {
    "id": "2080177355906007250",
    "text": "BIG OIL 2Q EARNINGS: TotalEnergies opens the earnings season with a beat (adj net income of ~$6 billion, up 68% y-on-y) thanks to high prices, trading profits, and refining margins. It's likely to become the theme of the season. $TTE keeps buyback at $1.5 bn for the quarter. https://t.co/CwnEpqV7Zp",
